{"tid":1577012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁定邦：監警會未有收到涉警員無編號的投訴","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T14:53:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae1d4ef7a719b201d7fbad6d53727b841dd1411","tid":1577012,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190917_20190917-205615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190917_20190917-205615.jpg&h=13e2d088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n監警會表示，就警方在反修例活動執法的投訴個案共有623宗，當中224宗是須向監警會匯報個案。主席梁定邦指，沒有收到直接投訴警員無編號的個案，但有投訴人未能提供警員編號，但他相信可以從現場片段等核實警員身份。<br />\n<br />\n警方在監警會例會上表示，就速龍小隊的制服設計未有位置顯示警員編號，已作出改善，在小隊頭盔上有識別編號，強調警方可透過編號，識別相關警員身份，又指可憑事發時間、地點比對值勤表識別警員。警方又透露，反修例風波至今有超過2200名警員及他們的家人，遭網絡「起底」，更有不少惡意恐嚇及攻擊訊息。<br />\n<br />\n警方的心理學家就指，警員執勤承受巨大壓力，6至8月有66宗警員及其家屬需要接受輔導的新個案。"},{"pid":"0407d43504cc03cb1c30fe05a230a69b104f7838","tid":1577012,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173091&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1173091%26csid%3D261_341&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Ag0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=a9cdbd60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173091&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0699bd23ed17dbea2bc9810428f931c768bd4e2c","tid":1577012,"uid":12405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8ae1d4ef7a719b201d7fbad6d53727b841dd1411","tid":1577012,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190917_20190917-205615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww